          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a kind of manual or treatise used for consultation and is a text on the rules (religious laws, Dharma) governing the removal of impurities, especially those related to pregnancy.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Āśaucanirṇaya</title>
              <title type="vernacular">आशौचनिर्णय</title>
              <author>
                <persName type="authority">Bhaṭṭojī Dīkṣita</persName>
              </author>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti bhaṭṭojidīkṣitakṛtāśaucanirṇayaḥ samāptaḥ / maṃgalaṃ bhagavānviṣṇur maṃgalaṃ garudadhvajaḥ / maṃgalaṃ praṇḍarīkākṣo maṃgalāya tanaṃ hariḥ / śāke 1708 bhādrapadaśuklāṣṭamyāṃ śukre yāmadvayena kṛto 'yaṃ lipinyāsaḥ / śubham // (f. 5v).</colophon>
            </msItem>
